vjxztprkblmhnsqowfiedcguay.name: Deadlifts
tips: Not keeping the bar close to the body
steps: Place a barbell on the ground in front of you.
Bend down and grab the bar with an overhand grip, hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart.
Lift the bar off the ground by straightening your hips and knees.
Lower the bar back down to the ground and repeat.

yvxzwpktnsqromjehbldgufcai.name: Tricep Dips
tips: Not keeping your body close to the bench
Not fully extending the arms at the top of the rep
steps: Place your hands on a stable surface behind you, such as a bench or the edge of a couch.
Extend your legs out in front of you and balance on your hands.
Lower your body down towards the floor by bending your elbows.
Push yourself back up to the starting position and repeat.

wxzyvptrsqonmkjehdglubfiac.name: Chest Flys
tips: Flaring the elbows out too wide
Not fully extending the arms at the top of the rep
steps: Lie down on a flat bench with a pair of dumbbells in your hands.
Extend your arms straight up over your chest, keeping a slight bend in your elbows.
Lower the weights out to your sides in a wide arc, keeping your arms straight.
Bring the weights back to the starting position and repeat.

asdaaaf.name: Barbell Squat
steps: Stand with feet hip-width apart
Grip the barbell with hands shoulder-width apart
Squat down by pushing hips back and bending knees
Return to starting position

asdasdf.name: Bicep Curl
steps: Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart
Grasp a pair of dumbbells with your palms facing forward
Keeping your elbows close to your sides, raise the weights towards your shoulders
Pause for a moment and then lower the weights back to the starting position
